WEBVTT

00:08:29.836 --> 00:08:33.844
This piece became a signature
of the Blue Man show.

00:08:35.410 --> 00:08:39.307
But we didn't throw out
all the rules of theater altogether.

00:08:39.331 --> 00:08:42.600
We had set designs.
We had lighting designs.

00:08:42.624 --> 00:08:44.885
We had a stage manager calling the shows.

00:08:45.601 --> 00:08:50.371
But I'm fairly sure
we were one of the very first shows

00:08:50.395 --> 00:08:54.459
that was connecting with our audience
in a respectful way,

00:08:54.483 --> 00:08:56.432
by hanging them upside down,

00:08:56.456 --> 00:08:58.930
(Laughter)

00:08:58.954 --> 00:09:01.146
dipping them in paint,